:: Create an account {"position":"475,650","size":"100,100"}
<% s.playerName = prompt("Enter your name:"); %>
<% s.botName = prompt("Enter your loved one's name:"); %>

[[Log In]]


:: Did anyone mention me? [speaker-bot] {"position":"900,1275","size":"100,100"}
<% if(s.personality == "kind"){ %>
We all do! We love you and miss you very much.
<% } 

else if(s.personality == "sarcastic"){ %>
Perhaps... we might miss you a little bit.
<% }

else if(s.personality == "grumpy"){ %>
Of course you'd ask. Yes. We miss you. 
<% }

else if(s.personality == "extroverted"){ %>
Of course! We miss you and can't wait to see you soon
<% } %>

[[I miss you too.]]
[[Tell everyone I say hello.]]


:: Everyone? [speaker-bot] {"position":"900,1150","size":"100,100"}
<% if(s.personality == "kind"){ %>
Of course! You know we're always together.
<% } 

else if(s.personality == "sarcastic"){ %>
Yeah. Who else would I be with?
<% }

else if(s.personality == "grumpy"){ %>
Yep.
<% }

else if(s.personality == "extroverted"){ %>
Of course! You know we're always together
<% } %>

[[Where?]]
[[Did anyone mention me?]] 


