:: I miss you too. [speaker-bot] {"position":"900,1400","size":"100,100"}
<% if(s.personality == "kind"){ %>
We are so proud of you.
<% } 

else if(s.personality == "sarcastic"){ %>
We are pretty proud of you.
<% }

else if(s.personality == "grumpy"){ %>
