:: Start {"position":"600,400","size":"100,100"}
GriefBot is a piece of digital speculative fiction that explores the up-and-coming field of AI-assisted deathbots. 

As we speak, companies are harnessing AI to help grieving people create these bots (for a fee, of course). You will "converse" with the bot by selecting conversation prompts. Be thoughtful with what you pick... your choices will matter in the end!

[[Play]]


